nodes.text: Inya Prime was a terrestrial astronomical object. While searching for allies of the Resistance around 34 ABY, Resistance operatives Shriv Suurgav and Zay Versio visited Inya Prime, where Suurgav acquired a persistent rash. Surgaav still had the rash when he and Versio returned to the Resistance, and remarked upon it several times.
Inya Prime was mentioned in the novel Resistance Reborn, written by Rebecca Roanhorse and published in 2019.
